{"tid":240023,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本旅行一問 及行程推介","createTime":"2017-05-12T06:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T16:24:38.000Z","uid":7387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85a4701c41b9549eed615a687a702a3d672805ac","tid":240023,"uid":7387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"小妹黎緊六月會第一次去日本玩<br />\n但係啲pass個啲搞到我頭都大埋<br />\n如果我一日既行程係咁<br />\n由關西機場--&gt;京都--&gt;伏見--&gt;宇治--&gt;京都<br />\n<br />\n咁我應該買JR one day pass再另外買ICOCA 定 <br />\n直接買haruka套票 好啲<br />\n重點係想慳錢<br />\n<br />\n另外大家有無啲咩行程推介<br />\n同好嘢一定要食架？<br />\n自己一個plan行程plan得好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7462c2bfb0b8dbffb32dbcc5ac6af23d82c8fd3","tid":240023,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"唔去最慳錢。"},{"pid":"e5b320846f3548cfbea01b98025ad65c8a967eb8","tid":240023,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"dl個乘換案內app <br />\ncheck下大約每程車錢<br />\n加埋睇下邊個抵d<br />\n就咁睇你一日都唔使坐好多程"},{"pid":"7ac9471085ffe216805afcb3d4663f126f06dc47","tid":240023,"uid":39171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"燒肉一丁&amp;天地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f9d0cfc988941e6aca24b1b4c01a7a20394dd7","tid":240023,"uid":7387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dl個乘換案內app <br />\ncheck下大約每程車錢<br />\n加埋睇下邊個抵d<br />\n就咁睇你一日都唔使坐好多程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你呀 其實我有個app<br />\n不過人蠢 計極都唔知點先平啲<br />\n不過依架應該買jr pass<br />\n我Klook買滿200減100<br />\n咁樣好似平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e26dbb6697a280c1ae32b37e200a17e2c57bcd","tid":240023,"uid":7387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒肉一丁&amp;天地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好 等我mark低先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概係邊頭架？"},{"pid":"31cb45d8b7d2d4ee739e06a3c98755676e8b0fa7","tid":240023,"uid":91620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"係香港生活已經成隻狗咁 依加去旅行都仲要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02691fdee2e19af52842751ebb07d5b57f87ddc5","tid":240023,"uid":79421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係關西玩我會推薦關西周遊卡，5千2yen好抵玩"},{"pid":"aaa90d6cfc08698cf158f0d3563c9d7975a7beec","tid":240023,"uid":113700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒肉一丁&amp;天地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天地人算吧啦，食過一次冇下次，D肉又鞋又un <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e554abd3670142c88460e6a039c7c8d8409f2","tid":240023,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"我第一日落機買海遊南海pass 住大阪 嵐山玩一日 京都玩兩日 2500yen pass大阪景點玩一日  最後果曰大阪shopping 中間去京都果邊全部去程買票坐新幹線+500yen巴士任搭 想省錢就坐阪急電鐵 但我省時間就新幹線11分鐘京阪來回 價錢好似單程千四円到"},{"pid":"abb8f103b925a9f66bbecfef5149413e3d00e01e","tid":240023,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"我伏見五點先去到 個感覺正好多 睇埋晚景 同埋少人好多"},{"pid":"684c9b615669451698eb9fe3eb7f488b76d5f9b3","tid":240023,"uid":7387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港生活已經成隻狗咁 依加去旅行都仲要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢青無錢 <br />\n惟有慳下車錢 留返啲錢食同買"},{"pid":"8ad8ae8ddb37061e8619fe7e8e0a8b8c35